
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <% provide(:title, 'Home') %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <% if signed_in? %>
        <div class="jumbotron">   
          <h1><%= gravatar_for current_user %></h1>
          </br>
          <h4>News feed</h4>
          </br>
          <div class="table-responsive">
            <table class="table table-hover"> 
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td><i class="pull-right fa fa-edit"></i> Today, 1:00 - trangvt liked your post.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><i class="pull-right fa fa-edit"></i> Today, 12:23 - thutt liked and shared your post.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><i class="pull-right fa fa-edit"></i> Today, 12:20 - You posted a new minmap entry title "How can we complete this app?".</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><i class="pull-right fa fa-edit"></i> Yesterday - longdh want to improve your mindmap name "abc".</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><i class="pull-right fa fa-edit"></i> 2 Days Ago - tienpx accept your request to improve his mindmap name "xyz".</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><i class="pull-right fa fa-edit"></i> 2 Days Ago - tronglvq liked your post.</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% else %>
        <div class="jumbotron">
          <h1>Welcome to MindMap App!</h1>
          <p>An optimized annotation tools, which we use both hemispheres to remember the world. </p>
          <%= link_to "Sign up now", new_user_path, class: "btn btn-large btn-primary" %>
        </div>
     
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <h2>Create</h2>
            <p>The fast way to express your ideas via mindmap diagram.   </p>
           <p><a class="btn btn-default" href= "https://github.com/tienpx/Nhom12_K57CA/wiki/How-to-create-a-mind-map" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-4">
            <h2>Share</h2>
            <p>The easy way to share your mindmap to your friends and invite them to develop it.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="https://github.com/tienpx/Nhom12_K57CA/wiki/How-to-share-your-mind-map-and-invite-your-friend-to-develop-it." role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
         </div>

          <div class="col-md-4">
            <h2>Save</h2>
            <p>The convenient way to save your mindmap in local devices as well as in web store.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="https://github.com/tienpx/Nhom12_K57CA/wiki/How-to-save-your-mind-map-in-local-devices-and-web-store." role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div> <!-- /container -->
  </body>
</html>
